Source: postgresql-faker
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://gitlab.com/dalibo/postgresql_faker

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-faker
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-faker
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, postgresql-plpython3-PGVERSION, python3-fake-factory (>= 6.1.1), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fake data generator for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 postgresql_faker exposes the Python Faker library as SQL functions for
 generating realistic test, training, anonymization, and demonstration data.
